-- Soccer Players Ribery, Benzema Charged in Prostitution Case, Figaro Says
-- Steve Rhinds
-- 2010-07-20T18:59:20Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-20/soccer-players-ribery-benzema-charged-in-prostitution-case-figaro-says.html

          
          
             French soccer players Franck Ribery
and Karim Benzema were charged with having sex with an underage
prostitute today after being questioned by police, Le Figaro
reported, without saying where it got the information.  
 If convicted, the men face a fine of 45,000 euros and up to
three years in prison, according to the daily newspaper.  
          
          


  


        